    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311940/extras/0321376f28b9aa6d04ffcde5c4e82e6e.avif?t=1733876175\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311940/extras_big/0321376f28b9aa6d04ffcde5c4e82e6e.avif?t=1733876175 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入古罗马的世界，体验罗马经典棋盘套装。 这套装包含9套精心打造的棋盘，每一套都受罗马古典雕塑的启发。 从闪亮的金属到抛光的雪松木，每一颗棋子都自豪地站在自己的基座上，逼真地描绘了百夫长、皇帝和元老院官员。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完美适合欣赏古典雕塑艺术的棋手，罗马经典棋盘套装让每场比赛都成为对罗马力量和遗产的致敬。随着每一步，都能感受到历史的厚重，仿佛百夫长和皇帝在战场上对峙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311940/extras/b093da8c2dcad4055386d5f6f1612cbe.avif?t=1733876175\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311940/extras_big/b093da8c2dcad4055386d5f6f1612cbe.avif?t=1733876175 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以古罗马的力量与荣誉来下棋—用罗马经典棋盘套装在棋盘上引领你的帝国走向胜利！</p>",
